{"id": 1063, "genre": 1000, "title": "你买过哪些穿不出去的时尚单品？", "description": "一切显腿短腰粗个头矮的东西穿的都不是时尚，是情怀。（题图来自：Sergiy Maidukov）", "record_count": 3814, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152330UbMGo2fhOSiz7TYt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-22T01:00:44Z", "questions": [{"id": 944, "title": "你买过哪些穿不出去的时尚单品？", "content": "你买过哪些穿不出去的时尚单品？ \r\n", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 89443, "content": "跟风买了阔腿裤，但我穿着五五分哈比人", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125832ygmrjbDVBFd9ZpL6.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89488, "content": "百褶长裙，穿去约会，吃完饭小肚子一鼓显露无疑", "image": "img/option/option/2016070312595083lXmcjK1iYNHCzy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89489, "content": " 露肩针织衫，春天穿肩膀冷，夏天穿身上热", "image": "img/option/option/20160703152258sBPhRUgwH1T4l8nJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89494, "content": "冬天入了件粉晶大衣，不加滤镜就像阿依莲海报走出来的", "image": "img/option/option/2016070218331521e84jbqYpOn50PG.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89491, "content": "买了个超漂亮的choker，脖子短", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125904TAPcizbpYLHVI1qd.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89501, "content": "罗马绑带凉鞋，小粗腿化身斯巴达壮士", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125951Pl4mIu63QWo8vC0S.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89502, "content": "外穿睡衣，搭不好就是到处乱跑的病号", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183126GPwVB9CuO8qvzAKy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 89492, "content": "想赶时髦穿leggings出街 ，然而太考验腿型了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183127sgO3uxDzkjHFloX8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 90461, "content": "优雅的男人都有一件得体的风衣，但前提是个儿高", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125907PrTYxVl1DRZLuacK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 90470, "content": "买了据说是百搭的布洛克鞋，配啥都奇怪", "image": "img/option/option/2016070218303